{
  "stem": "19982.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were a lot of Polish people which they wanted to come with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the German Jews went to the English, and they said, those are not German Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Those are Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would let-- not let us go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They kept us at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And meantime, at night, the Polish Armia Krajowa-- this is the AK-- was shooting at us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one man-- which, which it was very hot in the wagons because it was-- and he went out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they shot him in his leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Polish Army was, was shooting at-- because they knew that those are Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyhow, they would not let us go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The German Jews went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the English would not let go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One thing which is in my memory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When the English officers said, the world doesn't know what kind-- good thing Hitler did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So again, the anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we went back to Wroclaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then there was-- we realized we said we were in the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then they came, the-- there was the Bricha.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they started to take a-- but we walked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So you couldn't take anything with you, just a little bit-- attache which you could hold in your hands.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's how we went illegally through the border through Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from Czechoslovakia-- from-- to Vienna, from Vienna to Czechoslovakia; from Czechoslovakia to Germany; [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] or perhaps to Czechoslovakia to Vienna, I don't remember-- must have been that because we were-- and then we came to Ainring, to a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Ainring was on the border of Austria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was in-- near Berchtesgaden, where Hitler had his palace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were in Ainring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at this time, people were crossing back and forth from Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
